name: Diminish Mishmash
description:
Be a proud Collector of this simple yet challenging game by Dr Abstract that tests spatial counting skills. The interactive NFT with its elegant interface is coded with ZIM - code creativity on the canvas!

Dr Abstract is the Founder of ZIM and inaugural member of the Gadget Minters at https://zimjs.com/gadgetminters. To find out more about making interactive NFTs with ZIM 
please visit https://zimjs.com/nft.
